It's raining

2
00:00:07.000 --> 00:00:08.066
The wind blew the window open

3
00:00:19.366 --> 00:00:20.333
It’s been seven years

4
00:00:20.733 --> 00:00:21.533
Still with that cowardly look

5
00:00:21.566 --> 00:00:22.733
of someone who did something against their conscience

6
00:00:34.733 --> 00:00:35.533
My son

7
00:00:36.500 --> 00:00:37.733
You’ve grown so much

8
00:00:41.566 --> 00:00:42.533
No matter where you are

9
00:00:43.933 --> 00:00:45.166
I will find you

10
00:00:48.866 --> 00:00:50.133
As for that disgusting cheating couple

11
00:00:50.666 --> 00:00:52.633
I will make them pay dearly

12
00:01:03.700 --> 00:01:04.433
Please leave

13
00:01:04.500 --> 00:01:06.433
I said no such person is in our school

14
00:01:07.266 --> 00:01:08.066
That can’t be,

15
00:01:08.466 --> 00:01:10.166
My son, he goes to this school

16
00:01:10.266 --> 00:01:11.700
He really is a student here

17
00:01:11.766 --> 00:01:13.266
Can you please check again for me?

18
00:01:13.500 --> 00:01:14.333
Check what?

19
00:01:14.366 --> 00:01:16.266
You’ve already looked through the list three times

20
00:01:16.300 --> 00:01:17.466
If he’s not there, he’s not there

21
00:01:17.766 --> 00:01:18.066
Move aside

22
00:01:18.100 --> 00:01:19.033
Don’t interfere with my work

23
00:01:19.900 --> 00:01:20.866
Director, you’re here!

24
00:01:21.333 --> 00:01:22.100
What’s going on?

25
00:01:22.533 --> 00:01:23.933
I think this woman isn’t mentally stable

26
00:01:23.966 --> 00:01:24.566
She brought a photo

27
00:01:24.600 --> 00:01:25.433
and came here to find her son

28
00:01:28.400 --> 00:01:29.266
Duan Jia Le?

29
00:01:30.333 --> 00:01:30.933
Duan Jia Le

30
00:01:31.300 --> 00:01:32.033
Where is he?

31
00:01:32.333 --> 00:01:33.933
He dropped out last month

32
00:01:33.966 --> 00:01:35.533
Before that, he often skipped school for no reason

33
00:01:36.600 --> 00:01:37.466
Why did that happen?

34
00:01:46.100 --> 00:01:46.533
Teacher

35
00:01:46.800 --> 00:01:47.866
Why did the boy drop out?

36
00:01:48.166 --> 00:01:49.433
He said it was due to health issues

37
00:01:49.466 --> 00:01:50.133
For the specific reason

38
00:01:50.166 --> 00:01:51.333
you should ask his father